{"tid":1446194,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"強烈譴責警員施放催淚彈期間出動警犬","createTime":"2019-08-11T14:48:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T12:06:16.000Z","uid":107060,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f24c6faf1f1fe977832de3abff0b8685bbf2400f","tid":1446194,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:48:32.000Z","msg":"【強烈譴責警員施放催淚彈期間出動警犬】<br />\n<br />\n在近日的連場示威之中，警方多次出動警犬，但警犬明顯受驚，難以控制，熱血貓民對此已感到極度不滿。<br />\n<br />\n今日（8月11日）下午5時許，警方於長沙灣警署附近施放催淚彈，期間現場竟然有身穿頭盔及面具的警員，拖著一隻警犬行出閘外。<br />\n<br />\n示威現場，即使有著充足的裝備，都可能受傷，更何況是毫無防護的警犬。<br />\n<br />\n熱血貓民強烈呼籲警方，停止所有暴行！<br />\n<br />\n（now新聞截圖）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cQKNsD8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcQKNsD8.jpg&h=7cf9f591&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ff6ad3d686baa58f5a8001fc9303649c55215d62","tid":1446194,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:08:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52b27ebba4d4aa4b10f819ffefb776aba7cb4186","tid":1446194,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:21:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4cd041b18c39c36cf2824bf1fb45d4b71ab169e","tid":1446194,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:01:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfee8c175fee5c3586d797b0405371ae1c012162","tid":1446194,"uid":257398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:02:39.000Z","msg":"屌你地班臭閪 自己一手一腳訓練出黎既你拖佢去呢啲地方？"},{"pid":"8ea95d5bbeacc3400c42f2c6dd5929a01d736ca2","tid":1446194,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:03:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60a005eb7744c4d67de0fd1a3869367e218c0022","tid":1446194,"uid":20